			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				It's not really as hard as it may seem. The named sisters on the island aren't ones you'd like to f with... they're all level 25. The merchants (the dwarf and the one in the hut) are near 40 or so, even harder. To get the belts, just wander the island, and waste the generic &quot;Sister of Erollisi&quot; that are quite common. They aren't terribly hard, since they only wield halberds so no dual wield tricks. And they have low factions. Just kill the pirates whenever they spawn on the island and your faction with the sisters will usually go UP or stay where it is. It's a great spot for quick cash around level 20. Greenies that always have 2 plat loot on them EVERY TIME. And quick respawns, as well.
				</font>
			</td>

